@startuml 16-search-sort
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Search Sort (Similarity <-> Recency)

actor User
participant "SearchResultsPage" as UI
participant "SearchApi" as SVC
participant "POST /api/search" as API
participant "AppDbContext" as CTX
database "pgvector" as DB

User -> UI: tap Sort, pick "Most recent"
UI -> UI: sort.set('recency')\npage.set(1)
UI -> SVC: search({ q, sort:recency, page:1 })
SVC -> API: POST
API -> CTX: CTE ... ORDER BY occurred_at DESC
CTX -> DB: SELECT
DB --> CTX: rows
API --> SVC: 200 { results, totalCount unchanged }
SVC --> UI: results
UI --> User: rows reordered newest-first\nmeta "N contacts matched" unchanged

@enduml
